{"id":185,"parent_id":158,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":185,"title":"Deuteronomy 27","subtitle":"","short_title":"Deut.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 27"],[".studySummary",["i","The children of Israel are to cross the Jordan, build an altar, and worship the Lord—They are the Lord’s people but will be cursed if they do not obey Him."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.1","order":"02.06.027.16594"},["b","1"],"And Moses with the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"elders"],"of Israel commanded the people, saying,",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"Keep"],"all the commandments which I command you this day."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.2","order":"02.06.027.16595"},["b","2"],"And it shall be on the day when ye shall pass over Jordan unto the land which the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God giveth thee, that thou shalt set thee up great",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"stones"],", and plaster them with plaster:"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.3","order":"02.06.027.16596"},["b","3"],"And thou shalt write upon them all the words of this law, when thou art passed over, that thou mayest go in unto the land which the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God giveth thee, a land that floweth with milk and honey; as the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"God of thy fathers hath promised thee."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.4","order":"02.06.027.16597"},["b","4"],"Therefore it shall be when ye be gone over Jordan,",["i","that"],"ye shall set up these stones, which I command you this day, in mount Ebal, and thou shalt plaster them with plaster."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.5","order":"02.06.027.16598"},["b","5"],"And there shalt thou build an altar unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God, an altar of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"stones"],": thou shalt not lift up",["i","any"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"iron"],["i","tool"],"upon them."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.6","order":"02.06.027.16599"},["b","6"],"Thou shalt build the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"altar"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God of whole stones: and thou shalt offer burnt offerings thereon unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God:"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.7","order":"02.06.027.16600"},["b","7"],"And thou shalt offer peace",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"offerings"],", and shalt eat there, and rejoice before the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.8","order":"02.06.027.16601"},["b","8"],"And thou shalt write upon the stones all the words of this law very plainly."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.9","order":"02.06.027.16602"},["b","9"],"¶And Moses and the priests the Levites spake unto all Israel, saying, Take heed, and hearken, O Israel; this day thou art become the people of the",["span.smallCaps",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"Lord"]],"thy God."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.10","order":"02.06.027.16603"},["b","10"],"Thou shalt therefore obey the voice of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God, and do his commandments and his statutes, which I command thee this day."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.11","order":"02.06.027.16604"},["b","11"],"¶And Moses charged the people the same day, saying,"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.12","order":"02.06.027.16605"},["b","12"],"These shall stand upon mount Gerizim to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"bless"],"the people, when ye are come over Jordan; Simeon, and Levi, and Judah, and Issachar, and Joseph, and Benjamin:"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.13","order":"02.06.027.16606"},["b","13"],"And these shall stand upon mount Ebal to curse; Reuben, Gad, and Asher, and Zebulun, Dan, and Naphtali."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.14","order":"02.06.027.16607"},["b","14"],"¶And the Levites shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"speak"],", and say unto all the men of Israel with a loud voice,"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.15","order":"02.06.027.16608"},["b","15"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"Cursed"],["i","be"],"the man that maketh",["i","any"],"graven or molten",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"image"],", an abomination unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", the work of the hands of the craftsman, and putteth",["i","it"],"in",["i","a"],"secret",["i","place."],"And all the people shall answer and say, Amen."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.16","order":"02.06.027.16609"},["b","16"],"Cursed",["i","be"],"he that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"setteth light by"],"his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"father"],"or his mother. And all the people shall say, Amen."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.17","order":"02.06.027.16610"},["b","17"],"Cursed",["i","be"],"he that removeth his neighbour’s",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"landmark"],". And all the people shall say, Amen."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.18","order":"02.06.027.16611"},["b","18"],"Cursed",["i","be"],"he that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"maketh"],"the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"blind"],"to wander out of the way. And all the people shall say, Amen."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.19","order":"02.06.027.16612"},["b","19"],"Cursed",["i","be"],"he that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"perverteth"],"the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"judgment of"],"the stranger, fatherless, and widow. And all the people shall say, Amen."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.20","order":"02.06.027.16613"},["b","20"],"Cursed",["i","be"],"he that lieth with his father’s wife; because he uncovereth",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"his father’s skirt"],". And all the people shall say, Amen."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.21","order":"02.06.027.16614"},["b","21"],"Cursed",["i","be"],"he that lieth with any manner of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"beast"],". And all the people shall say, Amen."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.22","order":"02.06.027.16615"},["b","22"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"Cursed"],["i","be"],"he that lieth with his sister, the daughter of his father, or the daughter of his mother. And all the people shall say, Amen."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.23","order":"02.06.027.16616"},["b","23"],"Cursed",["i","be"],"he that lieth with his mother in law. And all the people shall say, Amen."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.24","order":"02.06.027.16617"},["b","24"],"Cursed",["i","be"],"he that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"smiteth"],"his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"neighbour"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_24c"},"secretly"],". And all the people shall say, Amen."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.25","order":"02.06.027.16618"},["b","25"],"Cursed",["i","be"],"he that taketh",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"reward"],"to slay an innocent person. And all the people shall say, Amen."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.26","order":"02.06.027.16619"},["b","26"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"Cursed"],["i","be"],"he that confirmeth not",["i","all"],"the words of this law to do them. And all the people shall say, Amen."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.1a","order":"02.06.027.16620"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/church-organization"},"TG Church Organization"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.1b","order":"02.06.027.16622"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/12.33.33-37"},"Mosiah 12:33 (33–37)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.2a","order":"02.06.027.16624"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/4.3"},"Josh. 4:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.5a","order":"02.06.027.16626"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/2.7"},"1 Ne. 2:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.5b","order":"02.06.027.16628"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/20.25"},"Ex. 20:25"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.6a","order":"02.06.027.16630"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/8.31.30-32"},"Josh. 8:31 (30–32)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.7a","order":"02.06.027.16632"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sacrifice"},"TG Sacrifice"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.9a","order":"02.06.027.16634"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/5.8.5-15"},"Mosiah 5:8 (5–15)"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.12a","order":"02.06.027.16636"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/11.29"},"Deut. 11:29"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/8.33.33-35"},"Josh. 8:33 (33–35)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/45.16.15-17"},"Alma 45:16 (15–17)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.21"},"D&C 130:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.14a","order":"02.06.027.16638"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/33.10"},"Deut. 33:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.15a","order":"02.06.027.16640"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/curse"},"TG Curse"],"."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.15b","order":"02.06.027.16642"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/34.17"},"Ex. 34:17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/13.2"},"Hosea 13:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/13.12.12-14"},"Mosiah 13:12 (12–14)"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.16a","order":"02.06.027.16644"},["b","16a"],["span.small","HEB"],"esteems lightly, disgraces."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.16b","order":"02.06.027.16646"},["b","16b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/honoring-father-and-mother"},"TG Honoring Father and Mother"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.17a","order":"02.06.027.16648"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.14"},"Deut. 19:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.18a","order":"02.06.027.16650"},["b","18a"],["span.small","OR"],"misleads."],["div",{"id":"18b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.18b","order":"02.06.027.16652"},["b","18b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/19.14"},"Lev. 19:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.19a","order":"02.06.027.16654"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/24.17"},"Deut. 24:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"19b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.19b","order":"02.06.027.16656"},["b","19b"],["span.small","OR"],"justice due to."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.20a","order":"02.06.027.16658"},["b","20a"],["span.small","OR"],"her who is his father’s."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.21a","order":"02.06.027.16660"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.15.15-16"},"Lev. 20:15 (15–16)"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.22a","order":"02.06.027.16662"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.17"},"Lev. 20:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.24a","order":"02.06.027.16664"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/21.14"},"Ex. 21:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"24b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.24b","order":"02.06.027.16666"},["b","24b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.11"},"Deut. 19:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"24c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.24c","order":"02.06.027.16668"},["b","24c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/5.31.29-41"},"Moses 5:31 (29–41)"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.25a","order":"02.06.027.16670"},["b","25a"],["span.small","HEB"],"bribe.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.12"},"Ezek. 22:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/5.31.29-41"},"Moses 5:31 (29–41)"],"."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.26a","order":"02.06.027.16672"},["b","26a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/curse"},"TG Curse"],"."]]}
